gems.name: google-cloud-gke_multi_cloud-v1
gems.info: Anthos Multi-Cloud provides a way to manage Kubernetes clusters that run on AWS and Azure infrastructure using the Anthos Multi-Cloud API. Combined with Connect, you can manage Kubernetes clusters on Google Cloud, AWS, and Azure from the Google Cloud Console. Note that google-cloud-gke_multi_cloud-v1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-gke_multi_cloud instead. See the readme for more details.
